{"tid":614530,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"復活節去咗影相見識到攝影團嘅文化","createTime":"2018-04-02T15:15:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-08T04:28:29.000Z","uid":890,"like":23,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"b3aa09bc653ab6e27062d53f225c2037bd172341","tid":614530,"uid":890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T15:15:21.000Z","msg":"原本都覺得有啲地方 join 攝影團都幾方便<br />\n依家見識過就不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搵個阿伯著文族服食住口煙<br />\n一大班人擺晒陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n前面踎幾個後面企幾個<br />\n係個景點 block 住成條路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n領導叫啲人 ready 好就叫個阿伯食煙<br />\n叫個阿伯食慢啲<br />\n唔好咁大煙<br />\n後面截人嘅領隊就數 1至10<br />\n跟住就以為去咗紅地氈<br />\n機關槍式快門聲此起彼落<br />\n完咗就第二批人影<br />\n個個團友張相應該會係一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大滿足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有無人 join 過嗰啲攝影團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">圖為我去嘅景點之一</span></strong> <span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">有時間 share 多d</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/1/890/26313365747_be7b46aec4_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F1%2F890%2F26313365747_be7b46aec4_b.jpg&h=3cb86d7c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2326706600e8c2cf77e3b7d68da6355636858177","tid":614530,"uid":55656,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T15:45:08.000Z","msg":"kmdd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw, 想睇多D相"},{"pid":"d898536916698484d7bb9b57286943aae16b9a71","tid":614530,"uid":52968,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T15:49:40.000Z","msg":"想睇阿伯相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"093d82a84c20e792c0fc70fa8fd9efec28815327","tid":614530,"uid":33556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T15:55:42.000Z","msg":"kmdd<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41ea60091e9cfb7a115a8c5c1e535ef968e9c908","tid":614530,"uid":890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d898536916698484d7bb9b57286943aae16b9a71","tid":614530,"uid":52968,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T15:49:40.000Z","msg":"想睇阿伯相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T15:56:35.000Z","msg":"無影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我要影自己野<br />\n嗰度啲光得好少時間有<br />\n過咗就無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bf865b2cc3dafee6290b841997b77a8ae3678fe","tid":614530,"uid":63515,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T16:29:00.000Z","msg":"影相要自已發掘先有樂趣<br />\n<br />\n呢d影完都唔想話係自已既作品，跟本係做左按快門機器"},{"pid":"6b9e03f8248d6d58173a44779abe9ed32c250335","tid":614530,"uid":43239,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T10:22:56.000Z","msg":"可以射架啦DD"},{"pid":"61b386f334c8cf5b4a0eac4385cf2d428f3386c1","tid":614530,"uid":104769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T05:08:31.000Z","msg":"影相嘅係大dd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cefecd00e99e7de99dfff8a5df2d96b5dbd625e","tid":614530,"uid":44458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T06:23:45.000Z","msg":"呢d. 人像都要咁join團，真係失敗。。"},{"pid":"eba4c49ab870dcbe36057d7920aecafd4317c749","tid":614530,"uid":44458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-